{"questionId":"3726e079","correctAnswer":"24","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Factor the second equation","content":"Rewrite: $\\dfrac{24x}{ny}=\\dfrac{24}{n}\\cdot\\dfrac{x}{y}=4$."},{"title":"Combine and compute","content":"Substitute $\\dfrac{x}{y}=4$: $\\dfrac{24}{n}\\cdot 4=4$, so $\\dfrac{24}{n}=1$ and $n=24$.<br/><br/>The answer is <strong>24</strong>."}]}